    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 body_text_wrapper">
        <h4>drying</h4>
        <p>Avoid putting your jeans in a dryer if 
        you can help it. Heat will increase the 
        shrinkage. Drying out in open air is always 
        best—using clothespins, binder clips or laying 
        them out flat (so you don’t get a crease).
        </p>
